#circuitbreakersg day 34

HAPPY MOTHER’S DAY! 
I’m so blessed to have a mother who can cook/bake so well. I don’t have to worry about being hungry any day at home😭 Thank you Mummy. 
Rice dumplings from 佳记美食 Jia Ji Mei Shi @jiajimeishi. 
They are famous for their Yam Cakes (Orh Kueh) & they also have other chinese all day breakfast like Chee Cheong fan, Soon Kueh, Glutinous rice, Rice dumplings, Porridge and etc. It is always long queue at their stall located in Chinatown complex. Plus, it’s really affordable.

Got their rice dumplings - Pork rice dumpling (肉粽) and Nyona rice dumpling (娘惹粽). Thanks for the complimentary Glutinous rice for Mother’s day 🥰 
They are currently providing delivery service for selected locations during this circuit breaker period. Preorder is required, do order soon if you want to try. Check out their IG @jiajimeishi for more info. 
#stayhome
@tastebudstoday yes it is sweet, thank you! 😍
Was the nonya dumplings sweet? Happy Mother’s Day! 🙌🏻
@jxeats What are your plans for this week? 😊
Happy mother's day to your mum🙌 so great to have a mum who cooks well👍
@annieeatss 😍😍 hope u can get ur craving fix soon😋
